title: List Keep3rV1 (KP3R) as Collateral Asset
body:
## Summary

List Keep3rV1 (KP3R) as Collateral Asset.

**For**: List Keep3rV1 (KP3R) as collateral asset
**Against**: Do nothing

## Background

Diversity of token list has always been the advantage of C.R.E.A.M. Finance Lending. By continually listing new token like BOND, we increase this advantage of protocol and expand our influence to reach more people, allowing more and more hodlers to leverage their tokens in C.R.E.A.M. Finance.
author: 0xb6e362900B7113F246A7e1c17E9746b3B9C079dB
